Description:
While using Presto, making changes to the 'Show only' or 'Plug type' filters are applied without clicking the 'Apply' button.

Severity:
Medium

Steps to reproduce:
1 - Open Presto
2 - From the Map tab, open the filters menu
3 - Make a selection from 'Show only' or 'Plug type' then close the menu by clicking 'X'

Expected Result:
Once 'X' is clicked, the user is returned to the map without filters applied.

Actual Result:
Despite 'X' being clicked, the filters are still applied.(video included)

Workaround:
De-select any filters you do not want to be applied.
